OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780924280
OL,3,CMan arrested after reported crossbow
OL,4,Cshooting at the University of Surrey
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder, after reports of
OL,8,Fan individual being shot with a
OL,9,Fcrossbow at the University of Surrey.
OL,11,FThe suspect is a 21-year-old Saudi
OL,12,Fnational, who was a former student at
OL,13,Fthe university, and remains in police
OL,14,Fcustody.
OL,16,FThe shooting took place at Manor Park
OL,17,FStudent Village, in Guildford, at
OL,18,Faround 10am on Thursday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
