CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780924280
OL,3,CMan arrested after reported crossbow
OL,4,Cshooting at the University of Surrey
OL,6,FThe victim, a man in his 50s who works
OL,7,Fas part of the university's campus
OL,8,Fsafety team, was airlifted to hospital
OL,9,Fin London where he remains in a
OL,10,F'serious' condition.
OL,12,FA significant emergency services
OL,13,Fpresence remains at the scene,
OL,14,Falthough access to the Royal Surrey
OL,15,FCounty Hospital is unaffected.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
