CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780924280
OL,3,CMan arrested after reported crossbow
OL,4,Cshooting at the University of Surrey
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Jon Groenen said:
OL,7,F"I appreciate that this incident will
OL,8,Fcause concern amongst our local
OL,9,Fcommunities, and I can reassure that
OL,10,Fwe are not looking for anyone else in
OL,11,Frelation to this incident.
OL,13,F"We are working closely with the
OL,14,Funiversity as our investigation
OL,15,Fprogresses.
OL,17,F"The suspect was detained at the scene
OL,18,Fshortly after the incident and an
OL,19,Finvestigation is now underway to
OL,20,Festablish the circumstances of the
OL,21,Fassault."
